<h2>Contenteditable Elements</h2>
<p>Spell-checking also works on elements with <a href="/docs/attributes/contenteditable/"><code>contenteditable</code></a>. This is particularly useful for rich text editors where you want spell-checking on prose but not on embedded code blocks.</p>

